Big Brother Naija 2018 housemate, Bambam was on Monday night caught having sex with Teddy A in the bathroom Recall that just yesterday, the internet was agog with controversies surrounding the pair over sex However, viewers have gotten a clear answer as the pair were caught having sex in the toilet, thinking they were away from the cameras. Recall that Miracle said all housemates have had sex, especially in the toilet, and that was the reason for missing condoms.  Pictures and videos of the scene has thrown social media agog as Nigerians are worried over Bambam who they think is being used by Teddy A. Teddy A has a baby mama outside the house and a son.